#### ❗ GAP #2b: Tidak Ada Local Only Hotspot Mode (TRUE MESH ENABLER)

**Masalah**: CARAKA saat ini 100% bergantung pada WiFi Direct P2P dengan star topology. Tanpa WiFi router, device B dan C harus relay via A (GO).

**Solusi**: Implementasi Local Only Hotspot mode (dari pelajaran Meshrabiya):

```kotlin
// LocalHotspotManager.kt — NEW component for Phase 1
class LocalHotspotManager(private val context: Context) {

    private var hotspotReservation: WifiManager.LocalOnlyHotspotReservation? = null

    fun startLocalHotspot(onStarted: (String, String) -> Unit) {
        // Requires ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION + CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE
        val wifiManager = context.getSystemService(WifiManager::class.java)
        wifiManager.startLocalOnlyHotspot(object : WifiManager.LocalOnlyHotspotCallback() {
            override fun onStarted(reservation: WifiManager.LocalOnlyHotspotReservation) {
                hotspotReservation = reservation
                val ssid = reservation.wifiConfiguration?.SSID ?: "CARAKA-${UUID.randomUUID().toString().take(6)}"
                val password = reservation.wifiConfiguration?.preSharedKey ?: ""
                onStarted(ssid, password)
                // Share SSID+password via BLE advertising or existing LAN beacon
                // so other CARAKA nodes can auto-connect
            }
        }, null)
    }

    // BATMAN-style: broadcast originator message via UDP multicast
    // so connected nodes know this device's virtual mesh IP
    fun broadcastOriginatorMessage(myMeshIp: String, hopCount: Int = 0) {
        val msg = """{"type":"ORIGINATOR","meshIp":"$myMeshIp","hops":$hopCount}"""
        // Send to 255.255.255.255 UDP broadcast on LAN
    }
}
```

