#### 1.1 Transport Layer Upgrade (Revised berdasarkan Riset 2026)

**Referensi Implementasi**: Meshrabiya (GitHub: UstadMobile/Meshrabiya), Bitchat Android

```
STRATEGI TRANSPORT STACK (berdasarkan riset mendalam 2026):

── LAYER 1: DATA TRANSPORT ─────────────────────────────────────────

Priority 1A: LAN UDP (existing) — jika ada WiFi router ✅
  → Sudah berjalan di Phase 0: LAN UDP port 8890
  → Any-to-any communication, tidak ada star topology
  → Bandwidth: theoretically 50-200Mbps

Priority 1B: Local Only Hotspot + BATMAN routing (NEW — Phase 1)
  → Setiap device buat hotspot DAN connect ke hotspot lain secara bersamaan
  → BATMAN originator messages: broadcast IP + routing info
  → Referensi: UstadMobile/Meshrabiya (open source, Apache 2.0)
  → Throughput: 300Mbps+/hop, 130-150Mbps multi-hop
  → API 26+, STA+AP concurrency required (most Android 10+)
  → SOLUSI PERMANEN untuk star topology problem

Priority 2: WiFi Direct (existing) — offline fallback saat tidak ada hotspot support
  → TCP socket, existing MeshSocketManager ✅
  → Tetap primary untuk device Android < 10 atau yang tidak support STA+AP

── LAYER 2: DISCOVERY ──────────────────────────────────────────────

Discovery A: WiFi Aware (NAN) — low-power proximity discovery
  → Check: WifiAwareManager.isAvailable() WAJIB sebelum gunakan
  → HANYA untuk discovery + control messages (<255 bytes)
  → Max ~5 concurrent data paths (Pixel hardware limit)
  → JANGAN gunakan sebagai primary data transport!
  → Trigger WiFi Direct / hotspot connection dari sini

Discovery B: BLE advertising — universal fallback discovery
  → Beacon interval: 250ms saat aktif, 1000ms saat idle
  → Payload: peerId, displayName, role (truncated)
  → Existing DNS-SD sebagai backup untuk WiFi Direct pairing

── LAYER 3: FALLBACK TRANSPORT ─────────────────────────────────────

BLE GATT Mesh — jika WiFi tidak tersedia (pendekatan Bitchat)
  → Max 6-7 concurrent GATT connections (Bluedroid hard limit)
  → MTU: 512 bytes, throughput: ~100-300kbps per koneksi
  → TTL-based flooding: TTL=10 (sedikit lebih dari Bitchat TTL=7)
  → Store-and-forward: simpan pesan untuk offline peers
  → Priority: SOS messages relay tanpa delay
  → Battery: ~3-5%/jam (vs WiFi Direct ~15-20%/jam)
  → TIDAK menggunakan Nordic nRF Mesh Library (itu untuk IoT nodes)
  → Implementasi custom BLE GATT server/client seperti Bitchat

── AUTO-FAILOVER ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

class TransportBridge(private val context: Context) {
    fun sendMessage(msg: CarakaMessage) {
        when {
            lanConnected           -> lanUdpTransport.send(msg)
            localHotspotActive     -> hotspotMeshTransport.send(msg)
            wifiDirectConnected    -> wifiDirectTransport.send(msg)
            bleConnected           -> bleGattTransport.send(msg.truncate(512))
            else                   -> messageQueue.enqueue(msg)
        }
    }

    fun selectTransportForMessage(msg: CarakaMessage): Transport {
        return when {
            msg.type == "SOS"      -> priorityTransport()  // semua transport, broadcast
            msg.size > 10_000      -> highBandwidthOnly()  // WiFi only, untuk voice
            batteryLevel < 20      -> bleTransportOnly()    // hemat baterai
            else                   -> defaultTransport()
        }
    }
}

── BATTERY OPTIMIZATION ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  Battery < 50%: turunkan beacon interval ke 1000ms
  Battery < 20%: switch ke BLE-only mode, suspend WiFi Direct
  Battery < 10%: passive-only (hanya terima, tidak relay)
  Authority device: TIDAK ada battery-based degradation (prioritas jaringan)
```

