#### 1.2 Real PKI (Ganti Hardcoded Demo Passwords)

```
PHASE 1.2 IMPLEMENTASI:

1. AuthorityCredentialManager.kt
   - Generate Ed25519 keypair saat pertama kali pilih role Authority
   - Simpan private key di Android Keystore (TEE-backed hardware security)
   - Public key = identity di mesh network

2. QR Code Exchange (ZXing)
   - Generate QR berisi: { publicKey, role, deviceId, signature }
   - Scan QR dari authority device → verify signature → store sebagai trusted
   - In-person verification = face-to-face trust establishment

3. Credential Expiry
   - Authority credential valid 30 hari
   - Warning 3 hari sebelum expired
   - Re-verification via QR dari device lain yang already trusted

4. Revocation (sederhana)
   - REVOKE packet broadcast via mesh
   - Semua node yang menerima = blacklist credentialId tersebut
```

